urdu transliteration text:
Sar Tan Se Juda Hote Hi Zainab Ye Pukari
Quran Bhala Hamse Juda Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC

Sadiyon Se Isi Sauch Me Gham Karbobala Thi
Hun Khaak Mujhe Khaake Shifaa Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC

Darkaar Hai Mazloom Aseero Ko Rehayi
Yeh Kaam Sakina Ke Siwa Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC

Ham Jaate Hain Zindaan Se Ay Baali Sakina
Roshan Teri Turbat Pe Diya Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC

Bhaiyon Ki Mazaraat Pe Bibi Ne Kaha Tha
Ab Hamse Ulajne Ki Khataa Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC

Ye Khutba E Zainab Ki Sada Bol Rahi Hai
Hai Kaun Sitamgaar Jafaa Kaun Karega
@HujjatELC
